{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/iko-uwais-dave-bautista-film-stuber/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Iko Uwais Melawan Dave Bautista di Film Stuber!","content":"<p>Apa persamaan antara Iko Uwais dan Dave Bautista? Ada banyak! Pertama, mereka adalah atlit bela diri â€“ Iko adalah pesilat, sementara Bautista lebih dulu terkenal sebagai Batista di ring gulat WWE. Kedua, mereka juga adalah aktor.</p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/3hYsVqpiEa4\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Ketiga, mereka sama-sama punya film yang melambungkan nama mereka di kancah perfilman internasional. Jika Iko Uwais populer sebagai polisi <em>hard-boiled</em> Rama dalam film The Raid, maka Bautista juga sama populernya sebagai Drax di Guardians of the Galaxy. Keempat, mereka pun sama-sama sukses di film lain. Misalnya saja Iko yang punya peran sentral di Beyond Skyline atau cameo unik di Star Wars: The Force Awakens. Kemudian, Bautista juga tampil memukau sebagai Hinx di Spectre, dan Sapper Morton di Blade Runner 2049.</p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/aZ9Os8cP_gg\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Iko Uwais dan Dave Bautista: dua orang dengan berbagai kesamaan dalam segi karir dan kemampuan. Apa jadinya jika mereka berdua bertemu dalam satu film? Jawabannya adalah Stuber, sebuah film aksi komedi yang kini tengah digarap 20<sup>th</sup> Century Fox.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45802\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45802\" data-attachment-id=\"45802\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/iko-uwais-dave-bautista-film-stuber/attachment/01-stuber/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/01-stuber.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-stuber\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/01-stuber-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/01-stuber.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45802\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/01-stuber.jpg\" alt=\"01 stuber\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/01-stuber.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/01-stuber-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45802\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: EW</p></div></p>\n<p>Iko Uwais dan Dave Bautista dipastikan terlibat dalam film Stuber yang saat ini masih berada dalam fase pra produksi. Bautista akan bermain sebagai seorang detektif tangguh yang membajak mobil milik supir Uber yang diperankan Kumail Nanjiani.</p>\n<p>Lalu, peran seperti apa yang didapatkan oleh Iko? Belum ada kejelasan soal peran Iko dalam Stuber, namun ada kemungkinan ia mendapatkan peran antagonis. Hmmm, jadi penasaran seperti apa akting Iko saat harus berperan sebagai seorang penjahat?</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45803\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45803\" data-attachment-id=\"45803\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/iko-uwais-dave-bautista-film-stuber/attachment/02-stuber/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/02-stuber.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-stuber\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/02-stuber-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/02-stuber.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45803\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/02-stuber.jpg\" alt=\"02-stuber\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/02-stuber.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/02-stuber-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45803\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Linggapos</p></div></p>\n<p>Keduanya pun saat ini nampak dalam kondisi cukup prima. Bautista baru saja merampungkan beberapa filmnya, termasuk <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/mengupas-trailer-official-avengers-infinity-war-lebih-dalam/\">dua film Avengers</a> yang segera tayang. Sementara itu, Iko juga sama-sama selesai dengan film Triple Threat (bersama Tony Jaa dan Tiger Chen), serta Mile 22 (bersama Mark Wahlberg dan John Malkovich).</p>\n<p>Film Stuber berawal dari naskah yang ditulis Tripper Clancy, yang kemudian dibeli oleh Fox. Michael Dowse didapuk sebagai sutradara. Karena saat ini Stuber masih dalam tahap pra produksi, jangan harap bakal ada berita besar dalam waktu dekat.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45804\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45804\" data-attachment-id=\"45804\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/iko-uwais-dave-bautista-film-stuber/attachment/03-stuber/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/03-stuber.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-stuber\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/03-stuber-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/03-stuber.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45804\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/03-stuber.jpg\" alt=\"03-stuber\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/03-stuber.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/03-stuber-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45804\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Michael Dowse. (Sumber: CBC)</p></div></p>\n<p>Tapi, coba bayangkan seperti apa jadinya jika Iko dan Bautista memang benar-benar mengadu kemampuan akting dan tarung mereka di depan kamera. Saya bisa membayangkan seperti apa keseruan pertarungan antara mereka. Iko dengan teknik silatnya, dan Bautista yang mengandalkan kekuatan fisik dan ketangguhannya semasa bergulat.</p>\n<p>Pertarungan mereka bakalan sangat sengit, dengan Iko memanfaatkan ukuran tubuh Bautista. Gerakannya lebih cepat dan luwes, namun tetap bertenaga. Dan karena Stuber juga merupakan film komedi, mungkin karakter Bautista akan gagal melayangkan pukulan pada Iko, lalu terjatuh dengan gaya super komikal.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45805\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45805\" data-attachment-id=\"45805\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/iko-uwais-dave-bautista-film-stuber/attachment/04-stuber/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/04-stuber.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-stuber\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/04-stuber-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/04-stuber.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45805\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/04-stuber.jpg\" alt=\"04-stuber\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/04-stuber.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/04-stuber-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45805\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Duniaku</p></div></p>\n<p>Apapun itu, kemunculan Iko Uwais bersama Dave Bautista dalam film yang sama patut kita tunggu. Apa film ini langsung masuk daftar tontonan kamu di masa depan?</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"24b0c6e7-1fbb-5bed-9638-a72ec1441d84"}}}